Minimum System Requirements:

System: PII 400 or equivalent
RAM:64 MB RAM
CD-ROM: 4X CD-ROM
Video Memory: 16 MB VRAM
Hard Drive Space: 580 MB
Mouse: Yes
Sound Board: Yes
DirectX: DirectX v7.0

Recommended System Requirements:

System: PIII 500 or equivalent
RAM: 128 MB RAM
CD-ROM: 8X CD-ROM

Game Description:

[b][i]The Wonderland that you knew from childhood has gone horribly wrong, and only you, Alice, can change it back! Based on the Quake 3 engine, this game looks gorgeous; it features a third-person perspective, horrifying creatures, and fantastic environments that can only be found in the Wonderland. However, note that this is NOT a child's game! It is as mature as they come.
